text: Einar Sörensen (26 July 1875 - 23 August 1941) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual and team épée events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1875 births Category:1941 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish épée fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
